sub_title: Honors Student at Leiden University College
summary: I am an energetic, ambitious Student of Liberal Arts majoring in Culture, History and Society, with a particular focus on Journalism and the Arts. I'm highly passionate about intersectional feminism and environmentalism, as well as topics surrounding equity and social justice and I am very eager to learn through experience. Currently I'm the chair of 22fm, a weekly radio show on different musical topics, as well as a board member of the analogue photography committee at my university.
